»CL0:Michael Summary Comments:

It was a case of getting your priority
right! And I am afraid to say that
»CL8:Freezers Uk» never. Just say that we
»CL9:had» joined »CL8:Freezers» 100%. Look at the
amount of changes we would of have to
do. For instance, »CL4:Chip Attack 2»
pictures and logos (I dont think
»CL8:Boo/Talent» & »CL8:Jade» would've been happy)
secondly, »CL4:Deadlock Magazine»! »CL8:Shade»
was reluctant in helping with the Gfx,
And it was a case of contacting
overseas division for help, and this
is where time consuming come into it!
The way how I see it, is everyone
should've been helping and that wasn't
the case at all. All we had to our
name, or shall I say or them had to
their name was? One cancelled Intro, a
person going around writing texts on
the bbs over hyping the team, an
artist sleeping on two jobs, a divided
sector within the Uk division, no
information, No planning and lastly no
communication! 
I will be of course writing my own
judgement about »CL8:Freezers Uk» in the
next »CL8:Deadlock!» This article was a
»CL1:joint venture» between all »CL8:Anathema»
members, and has been approved by
myself (»CL8:Michael»)! 
